Amelia Helen Womack (born 12 January 1985) is a British politician serving as Deputy Leader of the Green Party of England and Wales since 2014.
She served as Deputy Leader of the Green Party of England and Wales alongside Shahrar Ali from 2014 to 2016. She was re-elected in September 2016, once again in September 2018 and then again in September 2020. Womack stood as her party's lead candidate in the South Wales East region in the 2021 Senedd election.
